Reports.Name: Albert Utryckningar

Reports.Sql:
SELECT   

distinct  Convert(varchar(20),create_time,120) AS Inkom, 
          Convert(varchar(20),route_req_time,120)  AS 'Till väntelista', 
          Convert(varchar(20),contact_established_time,120)  AS Besvarat, 
          Convert(varchar(20),close_time,120)  AS Avslutat,  
Convert(varchar(10),DATEADD(second, Datediff(second,route_req_time,contact_established_time),'2015-01-01 00:00:00'),108) AS Svarstid,  
Convert(varchar(10),DATEADD(second, Datediff(second,contact_established_time,close_time),'2015-01-01 00:00:00'),108) AS Samtalstid,
                      source_address AS 'Samtal Från', destination_party AS 'Besvarat av', 
                      errand_desc AS Ingång, cg_hist_contact_log.errand_id, destination_address, 
                      target_domain, release_type 

FROM         cg_hist_contact_log INNER JOIN
                      cg_adm_errand ON cg_hist_contact_log.errand_id = cg_adm_errand.errand_id 
where create_time between (@datefrom) and (@dateto)


and errand_desc like 'K-%' 
and stop_date is NULL 
and target_domain IS NOT NULL


or create_time between (@datefrom) and (@dateto)
and errand_desc like 'KC #2%' 
and source_party IS NULL 

or create_time between (@datefrom) and (@dateto)
and errand_desc like 'KC #3%' 
and source_party IS NULL 
Order by Inkom
Reports.Name: Calls IN Kundtjänst

Parameters.Label: Nummer
Parameters.HelpText: Det går att söka på delar av numret. ex. %104587%

Reports.Sql:
SELECT     Convert(varchar(20),create_time,120) AS Inkom, 
           Convert(varchar(20),route_req_time,120)  AS 'Till anropskö', 
           Convert(varchar(20),contact_established_time,120)  AS Besvarat, 
           Convert(varchar(20),close_time,120) AS Avslutat, source_address AS 'A-nummer', 
           destination_party AS 'Operatör (ink.)',destination_address AS 'B-nummer', 
           target_domain AS Väntelista, release_type AS 'Avsluts Typ', 
Convert(varchar(10),DATEADD(second, Datediff(second,route_req_time,contact_established_time),'2015-01-01 00:00:00'),108) AS Svarstid,   
Convert(varchar(10),DATEADD(second, Datediff(second,contact_established_time,close_time),'2015-01-01 00:00:00'),108) AS Samtalstid
FROM         cg_hist_contact_log
where source_address LIKE @Nummer 
and create_time between (@datefrom) and (@dateto)
ORDER BY create_time DESC

SELECT   Convert(varchar(20),create_time,120) AS Inkom, 
		Convert(varchar(20),route_req_time,120) AS 'Till väntelista', 
		Convert(varchar(20),contact_established_time,120) AS Besvarat, 
		Convert(varchar(20),close_time,120) AS Avslutat,

FROM         cg_hist_contact_log INNER JOIN
                      cg_adm_errand ON cg_hist_contact_log.errand_id = cg_adm_errand.errand_id



where (cg_adm_errand.errand_desc like 'R- ICA%') 
and stop_date is NULL 
and source_party is NULL
and create_time between (@datefrom) and (@dateto)

SELECT DISTINCT 
                      CONVERT(varchar(20),system_test.effective_date,120) AS 'Lagd i provläge', CONVERT(varchar(20),system_test.expire_date,120) AS 'Tagen ur provläge', event_history.event_descr AS Händelse, 
                      test_category.testcat_id AS TestID, test_category.descr AS Testkategori, contact.first_name AS Förnamn, contact.last_name AS Efternamn, 
                      system_test.comment AS kommentar, system.panel_id AS Larmnummer,site.site_name AS Kund, site.site_addr1 AS Adress, site.city_name AS Ort, 
                      site.corpacct_servco_no AS Kundnummer, service_company.servco_name AS Namn
FROM         event_history INNER JOIN
                      system ON event_history.system_no = system.system_no INNER JOIN
                      system_test ON event_history.system_no = system_test.system_no INNER JOIN
                      contact ON system_test.contact_no = contact.contact_no INNER JOIN
                      site ON system.site_no = site.site_no INNER JOIN
                      test_category ON system_test.testcat_id = test_category.testcat_id INNER JOIN
                      service_company ON site.corpacct_servco_no = service_company.servco_no
WHERE     (system_test.effective_date > @datefrom) AND (system_test.effective_date < @dateto) AND (event_history.event_descr LIKE 'Lagd i%') 
  AND (system.cs_no LIKE '%-%') 
  AND (site.corpacct_servco_no = @kundnummer) 
AND site.cspart_no = '15'
ORDER BY 'Larmnummer'
